title: Extreme Networks Schedules First Quarter Fiscal Year 2016 Financial Results Conference Call and Webcast
text: Extreme Networks Schedules First Quarter Fiscal Year 2016 Financial Results Conference Call and Webcast Â» Science & Technology Published on 2015-10-08 06:45:55 Extreme Networks Schedules First Quarter Fiscal Year 2016 Financial Results Conference... -- SAN JOSE, Calif., Oct. 8,   Extreme Networks Logo Extreme Networks Logo  ><- stripped tags -> SAN JOSE, Calif. , Oct. 8,   Extreme Networks, Inc. (Nasdaq: [[]]), a leading provider of high performance networking solutions, today announced its plans to release the financial results for its first quarter ended September 30, 2015 , after the close of regular market trading on Thursday, October 29, 2015 , followed by an earnings conference call and webcast. The details for the webcast are: When: Thursday, October 29 th at 4:30 p.m. ET (1:30 p.m. PT). Where: Live over the Internet -- Simply log on to the web at the address above. Dial in: Toll Free: 1-(877) 303-9826 or international: 1-(224) 357-2194 Encore Recording: 1-(855) 859-2056 /or international 1-(404) 537-3406 Conference ID: 49772270 A replay will also be available for 7 days following the call. About Extreme Networks Extreme Networks, Inc. ( EXTR ) delivers software-driven networking solutions that help IT departments everywhere deliver the ultimate business outcome: stronger connections with customers, partners and employees. Wired to wireless, desktop to datacenter, we go to extreme measures for our 20,000-plus customers in more than 80 countries, delivering 100% insourced support to organizations large and small, including some of the world's leading names in business, education, government, healthcare, manufacturing and hospitality. Founded in 1996, Extreme is headquartered in San Jose, California . For more information, visit Extreme's website or call 1-888-257-3000.
